headline: Exclusive-TSMC pitched Intel foundry JV to Nvidia, AMD and Broadcom, sources say
summary: TSMC has pitched U.S. chip designers Nvidia, Advanced Micro Devices and Broadcom about taking stakes in a joint venture that would operate Intel's factories, according to four sources familiar with...
